title: B
description: Organisational area during the 'Heim ins Reich' resettlement events. The coordinates identify the seat (todays Bielsk Podlaski, wd:Q850714) of the commissioner, who was respnsible for the registration and resettlement of the Narew Germans (NS term: Deutsche aus dem Gebiet Bilsk) in the area of the Voivodeships Polesie (wd:Q2705666) and Białystok (wd:Q1305171). The polygon geometry roughly identifies this area with the Polish Border in 1939.
title_source: Die Umsiedlung der Wolhyniendeutschen in den Jahren 1939 bis 1940 (Stephan Döring, 2001)

title: Wo I
description: Organisational area during the 'Heim ins Reich' resettlement events. The coordinates identify the seat (todays Lutsk, wd:Q7550) of the commissioner, who was respnsible for the registration and resettlement of the Volhynian Germans (NS term: Wolhyniendeutsche) in the central area of the Wołyń Voivodeship (wd:Q1940320). The polygon geometries were derived by constructing Voronoi polygons around the seats within a predefined area covering Volhynia.
title_source: Die Umsiedlung der Wolhyniendeutschen in den Jahren 1939 bis 1940 (Stephan Döring, 2001)
